text: Cypsellurinae is a subfamily of flying fishes, one of four in the family Exocoetidae and the only one which is not monogeneric. ==Genera== The following four genera make of the subfamily: * Cheilopogon Lowe, 1841 * Cypselurus Swainson, 1838 * Hirundichthys Breder, 1928 * Prognichthys Breder, 1928 ==References== Category:Exocoetidae
title: Cypsellurinae
